DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20200415T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Special Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:The Board approved construction agreements for Roosevelt School
 's Building E and the 2950 Fair Oaks Avenue site as part of the Measure T 
 Bond Program\, adopted an updated bond budget\, and discussed paid leave p
 rovisions under the Families First Coronavirus Response Act.\n\nFull agend
 a and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2020-04-15/
