 anization and to evaluate the Superintendent's performance. In open sessio
 n\, the Board approved the 2023 School Accountability Report Cards\, accep
 ted labor proposals from both the Redwood City Teachers Association and Ca
 lifornia School Employees Association Chapter V\, and adopted Resolution N
 o. 6 regarding potential certificated employee reductions for fiscal year 
 2023-2024.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-
 02-07/
