  report. Approved the Second Interim Budget Report for 2023-24. Approved t
 he district transportation services plan\, PowerSchool analytics agreement
 \, and E-Rate bids for WAN and internet access.\n\nFull agenda and recordi
 ngs: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-03-20/
