 25. Board adopted the meeting calendar\, approved Measure U disbursements\
 , and ratified agreements for mental health services (Effective School Sol
 utions)\, after-school programs\, and community partnerships.\n\nFull agen
 da and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-06-20/
