DESCRIPTION:Board discussed the Facilities Master Plan progress and the pro
 cess for appointing an Area III trustee to fill a board vacancy. Public he
 aring confirmed sufficiency of instructional materials. Adopted resolution
 s for instructional material sufficiency and certificated tenure. First re
 ading of the board vacancy bylaw. Notably\, Board received information tha
 t they had decided against placing a parcel tax on the November 2024 ballo
 t.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-08-28/
