DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20240911T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board discussed Measure S bond program priorities with a focus 
 on HVAC replacements across the district. Heard an update on the Budget Re
 newal Initiative. Adopted Resolution 5 in favor of statewide Proposition 2
  (school facilities bond). First reading of Board Bylaw 9223 on filling bo
 ard vacancies. Reviewed charter school budgets.\n\nFull agenda and recordi
 ngs: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-09-11/
