 end assessment results for 2023-24. Continued the Area III trustee appoint
 ment process. Approved the 2023-24 unaudited actuals financial statement\,
  adopted the Gann Limit (Resolution 7)\, and approved teaching assignment 
 options (Resolution 6). Approved Measure U addendum for Garfield.\n\nFull 
 agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-09-25/
