 tion accommodation\, and school websites. Reviewed unaudited actuals for a
 ll three charter schools and the HR department's hiring season preparation
 s. Approved agreements with Redwood City Together and special education se
 rvice providers.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings
 /2024-10-23/
