  project and approved Resolution 9 for an energy services agreement with S
 outhland Industries. Heard an update on the workforce housing project at 7
 50 Bradford St. North Star Academy presented. Eight policy first readings 
 on school trips\, employee safety\, leaves\, modified duty\, and technolog
 y use. Adopted organizational meeting date and continued state preschool f
 unding.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-11-
 20/
