  and Alisa MacAvoy (17 years). Trustees-elect David Li and Jennifer Ng Kwi
 ng King sworn in\; Mike Wells re-elected and sworn in. Annual officer rota
 tion per Bylaws. Board reviewed California Dashboard local indicators and 
 approved the 2024-25 First Interim Budget Report. Consent items included R
 oosevelt Measure U addendum and annual developer fee report.\n\nFull agend
 a and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-12-17/
