SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Regular)
DESCRIPTION:Weekly and King absent (3-0 votes). Adopted the 2025-26 LCAP ($
 133.7M) and budget ($148.7M revenue\, $151.5M expenditures) — acknowledg
 ing $2.7M in deficit spending. Adopted Resolution 26 (Education Protection
  Account) and Resolution 27 (teaching assignments). Approved $21.25M for H
 VAC Phase II at Kennedy\, Orion\, and Clifford. Approved $2M Boys & Girls 
 Clubs and $1.08M PAL afterschool contracts. Bond consent: inspection/testi
 ng with Applied Materials and commissioning with Cypress Engineering for P
 hase 1 HVAC. Trustee Li reported attending SMCOE School Funding Task Force
 . Board retreat set for Aug 12.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcs
 d.info/meetings/2025-06-25/
