 essed new state laws: intervention in underperforming schools\, conduct/sm
 artphone restrictions\, suicide prevention\, English Learner education\, a
 nd homework/AI policy. Public comment: Carl Landers (Bond Oversight Commit
 tee) on AC rental unit funding. Adopted Resolution 10 (teaching assignment
 ) and Resolution 11 approving KIPP Excelencia's Prop 2 facilities rehab at
